---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<section
  class="flex flex-col-reverse md:flex-row-reverse w-full items-center justify-between gap-5 md:gap-20"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-between h-full gap-2 md:gap-10 md:w-[60%]">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-5xl font-bold">
      Looking for Property? We Can Help!
    </h1>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-darkGray text-center md:text-left"
    >
      At Rejoice Estate Consultants, we transform the real estate experience
      with innovative solutions and top-notch customer service. Whether you're
      buying, selling, leasing, or investing in properties in Mumbai's Western
      Suburbs, our expert team is here to help.
    </p>
    <p
      class="text-lg md:text-xl font-light text-darkGray text-center md:text-left"
    >
      <span class="font-bold"
        >Fill out the inquiry form below for personalized assistance</span
      >, detailed property information, or to discuss potential business
      collaborations. One of our knowledgeable consultants will promptly reach
      out to address your needs and help you achieve your real estate goals. We
      look forward to partnering with you in making informed real estate
      decisions.
    </p>
  </div>
  <Image
    src="https://res.cloudinary.com/aryansharma/image/upload/v1722862809/findingHouse.jpg"
    width={320}
    height={209}
    alt="property in mumbai"
    class="w-full h-auto my-5 md:w-[40%] rounded-2xl shadow-xl border-2 object-cover"
  />
</section>
